    "headline": "Broadcom Ties Wi-Fi 8 And 5G To Future Broadband Growth Potential",
    "summary": "Broadcom (NasdaqGS:AVGO) and Samsung have introduced a broadband focused fixed wireless access reference platform that integrates Broadcom's Wi-Fi 8 SoC with Samsung's 5G modem technology. The companies describe this as an industry first solution designed to help mobile operators deliver high-speed, low-power broadband over wireless networks. Broadcom has also expanded its Wi-Fi 8 SoC portfolio for Ethernet routers and mesh Wi-Fi systems aimed at residential networking equipment. For...",
